name: I Love You 143 Friendship Bracelet - Solid Colors Cool
description:
This isn't just a super cute layering bracelet, it also communicates "I love you" in code. 
Years ago, my husband started using 143 as a code for I love you in notes, the numbers representing the amount of letters in the words.  So, when I wanted to design a special friendship bracelet I immediately thought of our code and incorporated it into the design. 
Bracelets make a great gift for sisters, best friends, mothers to daughters, you name it. Such a fun secret way to remind someone they are special to you!
Aqua, Mint or Emerald with gold plated bronze nugget beads. in 143 arrangement to say "I Love You". 7" finished length. 
(Price is for a single bracelet)
